{"tid":835834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖」五歲仔獨玩摩天輪 探頭外望變半天吊","createTime":"2018-09-25T08:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T08:53:39.000Z","uid":147987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4eef2ada41808c575ca0bfc9cce1a5a8dd4f55ad","tid":835834,"uid":147987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"浙江台州市一個公園，今早發生離奇意外。一名5歲男童獨自登上公園的摩天輪，當車廂轉到離地近40米半空時，男童往外探望時失去平衡，身體掛在廂子外，只有頭部卡在椅背與欄桿中間，差一點從天而降。工作人員見狀將車廂轉回地面，男童幸只受皮外傷，沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今早10時許，民眾指台州玉環公園內摩天輪，有一名小童掛在車廂外，初時男童拼命掙扎，後來漸漸不掙扎了，嚇得群眾驚呼。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員立即將車廂轉回地面，救下男童。現場消息指男童今年5歲，因他母親不捨得買票，男童便在沒大人陪同下，獨自登上摩天輪，然後當車廂升至半空時，他將身體探出窗外觀看，一時失去平衡，卡在椅背與欄桿中間，幸好他頭夠大，沒有滑落地面。"},{"pid":"9150b7218cb94d9ab8b9c6fb69c774d276c93102","tid":835834,"uid":195920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"d33172e189b9d7a0a08b98f51d8cc8ce9ee45605","tid":835834,"uid":147987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/161433_f5113505d5bb0f0a26ad43134bda347c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F161433_f5113505d5bb0f0a26ad43134bda347c.png&h=5191a970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54dd2f2fb951473b4e9b26f48275900692281c34","tid":835834,"uid":188542,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>「有圖」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/161440_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F161440_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=b85c9c62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a70007fbdd30f39e6bfe7806fae51fb0372f4b7e","tid":835834,"uid":188542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"Nevermind."},{"pid":"d9a